@startuml sequence_zapping_liba4tv
title Zapping - brodcast
' * akcesori getXxxControl() su na IDTVManager (interfejs nije zaseban u ovom javadoc subset-u) - potvrditi.
' TIS implementira ServiceListener i StreamComponentListener; callback-ovi = isprekidane strelice ka TIS.

actor User
participant "Live TV App" as App
participant "Broadcast TvInputService" as TIS
participant "IDTVManager" as MGR
participant "ComediaRouteManagerControl" as ROUTE
participant "DisplayControl" as DISP
participant "ServiceControl" as SVC
participant "StreamComponentControl" as SC

User -> App : Play channel 1
App -> TIS : onSetSurface(surface)
App -> TIS : onSetStreamVolume(0.0)
App -> TIS : onTune(channelUri)
TIS -> MGR : DtvControl.context().dtvManager()
note over TIS,MGR : kontrole iz IDTVManager*:\ngetComediaRouteManagerControl(), getServiceControl(),\ngetStreamComponentControl(), getDisplayControl()
TIS -> ROUTE : getLiveRoute(listIndex, serviceIndex, prevRouteId)
ROUTE --> TIS : liveRoute : int
TIS -> DISP : setVideoSurface(layer, SurfaceBundle)
TIS -> SC : registerListener(streamComponentListener)
TIS -> SVC : registerListener(serviceListener)
TIS -> SVC : startServiceByTriplet(liveRoute, listIndex, serviceIndex, onid, tsid, sid)
note over TIS,SVC : alternativa (file/IP izvor): zapURL(liveRoute, url)\npoziv je ASINHRON - rezultat stize preko listenera (~2-3 s)

SVC --> TIS : ServiceListener.channelChangeStatus(liveRoute, true, ServiceStateChangeError.OK)
SC --> TIS : StreamComponentListener.componentChanged(liveRoute, StreamComponentType)
SVC --> TIS : ServiceListener.safeToUnblank(liveRoute)
TIS -> App : video vidljiv + onSetStreamVolume(restore) (unmute)
TIS -> SVC : getActiveService(liveRoute) / getServiceDescriptor(listIndex, serviceIndex)
SVC --> TIS : ServiceDescriptor (getName, getONID, getTSID, getServiceId)
note over ROUTE : ispod liba4tv: route -> demux + dekoder (TDAL_AV -> MediaCodec/AudioTrack) - demo-level
TIS --> App : Service started -> Playback active
@enduml
